{"tid":1602353,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"29/9 [18:08] 【灣仔】有個阿叔聲稱睇到黑衫卧底放火 From 蘋果Live","createTime":"2019-09-29T11:24:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T16:40:33.000Z","uid":204194,"like":47,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"274dbec8339ce9f23051886c0cb7aa762e34e8fa","tid":1602353,"uid":204194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T11:24:28.000Z","msg":"簡介：有個阿叔話睇住黑衫卧底全程，雖然未有親眼目睹放火一刻，但佢話當轉角位(側門)有火後，一班黑衫卧底狗就係轉角位走出嚟，所以極度合理懷疑係黑衫卧底狗放。而黑衫卧底狗其後係防暴保護下入地鐵，再以同樣裝束上返地面。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/355t2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2F355t2&d=AXXoxpexL8qkFRpCGxAvLfkum5iQZutveDYoRIbm5C0%3D&h=9951f190\" target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/355t2</a>"},{"pid":"85aff1278e855689a3daa3ba8c5a1d173026d814","tid":1602353,"uid":107957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T11:24:58.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5e7ba8a40b6d8333255c9559bfb2ba684b002a4","tid":1602353,"uid":10712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T11:26:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c179fb678eb598c77bdfb9cad46749716b720ce1","tid":1602353,"uid":271434,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T11:27:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔知我有無聽錯，十月一日皇上閱兵期間，<span style=\"color: red;\">假如同一時間有遊行，係絕對唔會有清場行動。</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">聽講北大人唔想在世界各地直播閱兵期間，同時直播出現血腥鎮壓嘅場面，咁會落佢面，令皇上即時受到黨內外以及西方社會譴責</span>所以十一閱兵嘅時候唔會清場鎮壓。但之前上面會嚇窒唔俾大家出，但如果出咗佢都耐你唔何。<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">聽講呢個安排僅十一閱兵嘅時段限定！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">聽講十一閱兵期間嘅和平遊行，唔會有清場鎮壓！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1585568\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1585568</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">核彈！中共極懼怕網絡信息安全在國慶節前出事！兄弟們即刻行動香港可獲勝！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1574727\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1574727</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">十一遊行要高叫「習近平下台」口號落中共面！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1568634\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1568634</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有明確訊息證實係習近平一人當日堅持拒絕「撤回」及下令將44人極速起訴暴動！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1602129\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1602129</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4113bccbfcbf8f99785ebf0357e48d8431cb9db4","tid":1602353,"uid":204194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T11:28:15.000Z","msg":"此post目的係俾係比大家文宣彈藥，非捉鬼，但我個人覺得要知，要有一定程度上防範。"},{"pid":"eaade1a1245f26c2855ac723368f8a63718ed868","tid":1602353,"uid":204194,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T11:32:19.000Z","msg":"等手足脫險先再大推，期間小推，以免阻礙重要post"},{"pid":"c23c353959a342b4bdab76e1a5cdbc54ee29ea64","tid":1602353,"uid":76776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T11:33:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"344f675963bd948b3a08ed45844c68215f620b38","tid":1602353,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T11:34:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eed49c02139800f9b99c257cb1ab68989ec4e89e","tid":1602353,"uid":204194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c23c353959a342b4bdab76e1a5cdbc54ee29ea64","tid":1602353,"uid":76776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T11:33:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T11:36:02.000Z","msg":"live 中未有提供，希望記者有留contant 之類"},{"pid":"1d41d7bac2d58b193364b405a96e0a8900d17a29","tid":1602353,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T11:36:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"47b93270cb80810010e170062da56829d2aa7c2c","tid":1602353,"uid":86204,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cited